[32m│[0m redirects to index.html                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Findings                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Processing Endpoint**: `/send.php` is NOT a contact form page - it's a  [32m│[0m
