[32m│[0m successfully" - this is the confirmation page after form submission          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Technology**: Modern PHP 8.3.6 stack with Alpine.js frontend framework  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m (evidenced by `x-data` attributes)                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Application Structure Discovered                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Endpoints Found:**                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/send.php` - Contact form processor (POST only)                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `index.html` - Main landing page                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `signin.html` - Authentication page                                        [32m│[0m
