[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Form Processing Flow:**                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m index.html (contains contact form)                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m     ↓ POST to /send.php                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m send.php processes data                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m     ↓ redirects to                                                           [32m│[0m
