[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Critical Security Observations                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Direct Access Prevention**: The 302 redirect suggests basic access      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m control (no direct GET access to processor)                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **PHP 8.3.6**: Modern PHP version with improved security features         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Alpine.js Framework**: Frontend uses Alpine.js with `x-data` reactive   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m state management                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **No Session Cookies**: No session identifiers or CSRF tokens visible in  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m this request                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
